casebody.data:
First Department,

April, 1944.

(April 3, 1944.) Edward Sopkin, Respondent, v. Walgreen Company of New York, Inc., Appellant, et al., Defendants.

Order unanimously reversed, with twenty dollars costs and disbursements, and motion denied. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Townley, Glennon, Dore and Cohn, JJ.
